{"tid":2359640,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和合石石廠謀殺案 警方拘捕13男女　","createTime":"2021-01-09T05:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T05:59:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44cdb1e73cbbf5cb52f7eae03d27ca572fb2bb00","tid":2359640,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"和合石一間承造墓碑的石廠上月底(22/12)發生謀殺案，5名黑衣刀手突然闖入以牛肉刀狂斬57歲石廠東主彭毓宏，彭身中多刀浴血，送院死亡。新界北總區重案組接手調查接近3星期後破案，拘捕13男女涉嫌謀殺、販運危險藥物及藏有攻擊性武器，下午將交代破案詳情。<br />\n<br />\n事發上月22日早上11時47分，5名刀手闖入石廠辦公室，揮牛肉刀襲擊彭，他頭部、腰部及大腿近大動脈多處中刀倒地，刀手逞兇後登上接應的黑色七人車逃去，彭送院搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210109/VNZ67YTJVVHX5IHZKKKCON3A2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210109%2FVNZ67YTJVVHX5IHZKKKCON3A2Q%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=0560b02c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210109%2FVNZ67YTJVVHX5IHZKKKCON3A2Q%2F&h=ab565e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210109/VNZ67YTJVVHX5IHZKKKCON3A2Q/</a>"},{"pid":"6ba6ce9dddecee6411308f02101918327015dfa8","tid":2359640,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:31:11.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手去錯和合石？"},{"pid":"57e5e14bb186e60d1e8f581467b0eb53edaae000","tid":2359640,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"又話有国安法社會穩定？<br />\n5毛藍屍係咪準備話係黃絲斬人？"},{"pid":"b22a8be816e864498e8cb2025062ebed16996210","tid":2359640,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"石廠 = 骨灰龕（重大利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"279f02ef8158de74402e6ad41ed1c060538c7c08","tid":2359640,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"